{
  "page": "Magister",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg/350px-Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"286\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg/525px-Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fb/Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg/700px-Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a>, a magister of <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>, by Jake Murray © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Magister</b> is a title held by wealthy and powerful individuals in some <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>. It is similar to the <i><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qhoran&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Qhoran (page does not exist)\">qhoran</a></i> or <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Steward\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Steward\">steward</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Magisters have kept records of their cities since their foundations as freeholds during the time of <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyria</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafother_lands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafother_lands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Magisters sometimes post <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> at their gates.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Magisters in <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Norvos\" title=\"Norvos\">Norvos</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> give lavishly to passing <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">khals</a></i> to convince the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> to continue on their way.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Free_Cities\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Free Cities</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Known_Magisters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Magisters</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#From_Pentos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">From Pentos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#From_Lys\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">From Lys</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Free_Cities\">Free Cities</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Free Cities\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Council_of_magisters_(Pentos)\" title=\"Council of magisters (Pentos)\">council of magisters</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>, nobles who elect the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Pentos\" title=\"Prince of Pentos\">Prince of Pentos</a>, are the practical rulers of the city.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_pentos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> They sometimes lend money.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>, magisters and <a href=\"/index.php/Keyholder\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Keyholder\">keyholders</a> participate in the election of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sealord_of_Braavos\" title=\"Sealord of Braavos\">Sealord</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>While <a href=\"/index.php/Lorath\" title=\"Lorath\">Lorath</a> is nominally ruled by <a href=\"/index.php/Princes_of_Lorath\" title=\"Princes of Lorath\">three princes</a>, the city is truly ruled by a <a href=\"/index.php/Council_of_magisters_(Lorath)\" title=\"Council of magisters (Lorath)\">council of magisters</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_lorath.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Council_of_magisters_(Norvos)\" title=\"Council of magisters (Norvos)\">council of magisters</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Norvos\" title=\"Norvos\">Norvos</a> is subservient to the <a href=\"/index.php/Bearded_priests\" title=\"Bearded priests\">bearded priests</a> of that city.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_norvos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_norvos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a> is ruled by a <a href=\"/index.php?title=Conclave_of_magisters_(Lys)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Conclave of magisters (Lys) (page does not exist)\">conclave of magisters</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a> is led by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Conclave_of_magisters_(Myr)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Conclave of magisters (Myr) (page does not exist)\">a conclave</a> as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Conclave_of_magisters_(Tyrosh)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Conclave of magisters (Tyrosh) (page does not exist)\">A similar group</a> chooses the <a href=\"/index.php/Archon_of_Tyrosh\" title=\"Archon of Tyrosh\">Archon of Tyrosh</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Triarchy\" title=\"Triarchy\">Triarchy</a> was ruled by a council of thirty-three magisters,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup> with <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a> each supplying eleven members.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Magisters, <a href=\"/index.php/Archon\" title=\"Archon\">archons</a>, and merchant princes of the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> initially welcomed <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> after they departed the <a href=\"/index.php/House_with_the_red_door\" title=\"House with the red door\">house with the red door</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>. The exiles ended up being hosted by <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> arranges <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Drogo_and_Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Wedding of Drogo and Daenerys Targaryen\">the wedding</a> of Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> outside <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Daenerys sees a ship named <i><a href=\"/index.php/Magister_Manolo\" title=\"Magister Manolo\">Magister Manolo</a></i> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Port_of_Qarth\" title=\"Port of Qarth\">port of Qarth</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a> sees a cog named <i><a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Magister\" title=\"Brave Magister\">Brave Magister</a></i> in <a href=\"/index.php/White_Harbor\" title=\"White Harbor\">White Harbor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Magisters\">Known Magisters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Magisters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"From_Pentos\">From Pentos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: From Pentos\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>The father of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyanna_of_the_Tower\" title=\"Tyanna of the Tower\">Tyanna of the Tower</a></li>\n<li>The host of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a> and his wife, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Laena_Velaryon\" title=\"Laena Velaryon\">Laena Velaryon</a> during their stay in Pentos in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_115_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">115&#160;AC</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_116_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">116&#160;AC</a>. The twins <a href=\"/index.php/Baela_Targaryen\" title=\"Baela Targaryen\">Baela</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Daemon)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Daemon)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a> were born at the magister's manse.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ordello\" title=\"Ordello\">Ordello</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"From_Lys\">From Lys</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: From Lys\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Bambarro_Bazanne\" title=\"Bambarro Bazanne\">Bambarro Bazanne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Torreo_Haen\" title=\"Torreo Haen\">Torreo Haen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tigaro_Moraqos\" title=\"Tigaro Moraqos\">Tigaro Moraqos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lysandro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysandro Rogare\">Lysandro Rogare</a>, who took the title of <a href=\"/index.php/First_Magister\" title=\"First Magister\">First Magister</a> for Life.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Gluttons are greedy men as a rule, and magisters are devious.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_17-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-17\">&#91;17&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Dany had seen <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> guards in the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>, posted at the gates of magisters, <a href=\"/index.php/Archon\" title=\"Archon\">archons</a>, and dynasts.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">My brother</a> visited <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>, near all the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>. The magisters and <a href=\"/index.php/Archon\" title=\"Archon\">archons</a> fed him <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> and promises, but his soul was starved to death. A man cannot sup from the beggar's bowl all his life and stay a man.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Arstan Whitebeard</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Magister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 33\">Chapter 33</a>, Tyrion VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafother_lands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafother_lands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Other Lands.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i